name: .XCWORKSPACEDATA File Extension
summary: Learn about .XCWORKSPACEDATA files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: XCWORKSPACEDATA files are not meant to be opened. Instead, Apple Xcode references the files to load the information they contain.
Since the files store XML information, you can open them with a text editor. However, opening them with a text editor will not appear the same as if opening them with Xcode.
